path.class: Alex has been using Catch for Tax Withholding for about a year. She was previously covered by her spouse Sams employer-provided health plan. Sam lost their job earlier this year. Given their uncertain financial outlook, the couple decided to go without health insurance. Unsure if Sam will return to a full-time job with benefits, theyre now considering a Marketplace plan.

After having been involved in a minor car accident years earlier, Alex and Sam understand how expensive medical bills can be. Their primary motivation is having coverage in case of an unexpected emergency, along with routine preventative care. Alex is also interested in starting therapy to cope with heightened anxiety.
Affordable monthly premium Access to mental healthcare
With Alex and Sam both working as contractors, theyre unsure how much theyll earn this year which makes it difficult to budget for health insurance.
